data.description: New Price! ***360-deg VIEWS!*** Beautiful 1.18-acres set on the rim w/ beautiful views of the valley below, mountains, gorgeous Idaho sunsets! Fully-fenced backyard, garden w/ producing raspberries, rhubarb, strawberries, and Concord grapes, plus peach, apple, pear, cherry, nectarine trees. Mature sycamore tree, lilac bushes, shade trees. Long, covered deck off the beautifully updated kitchen with new cabinetry, granite countertops, stylish farm sink, XL stainless steel refrigerator, sleek glass cooktop w/ elegant hood. Almost every inch of this home touched w/ updates, fresh paint, new kitchen/bathroom flooring, all new carpet downstairs, modern fixtures, comforts for peaceful country living. Enclosed multi-purpose breezeway leads to the spacious garage w/ extra depth and width for projects/storage. New wood stove and new pellet stove. And the cherry on top...the brilliant-red, XL chicken coop/enclosure.
